            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3 data-en="Quick Links" data-fa="دسترسی سریع">Quick Links</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#markets" data-en="Markets" data-fa="بازارها">Markets</a></li>
